{"tid":1595211,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"be birds 有無得用簡單規則創造複雜抗爭行為？","createTime":"2019-09-26T02:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T02:44:16.000Z","uid":22894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"74fe67afde2aa2d043309bc5c735ce4bb25a479b","tid":1595211,"uid":22894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:44:16.000Z","msg":"英文就叫 Flocking behaviour <br />\n中文就叫植絨行為<br />\n大意係雀仔只需要 3 條簡單規則<br />\n就可以創造到好複雜嘅群體飛行行為<br />\n期間完全無需同其他個體協調 各守本分就得<br />\n<br />\n究竟可唔可以參考雀仔<br />\n用幾條簡單嘅抗爭規則<br />\n去創造好複雜嘅抗爭行為呢？<br />\n完全省卻大台嘅問題之餘 又可以做到群體合作嘅效果<br />\n無往而不利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flocking_(behavior\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFlocking_%28behavior&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=9e022eba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flocking_(behavior</a>)"}]}